id: pmc-gn92
title: "Fix stale file path references in pm items (mjs → ts, dist → dist/cli.js)"
description: Keep pm item file references in sync with actual repo file paths to avoid pm validate warnings about missing linked paths.
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 0
