comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:11:30.262Z",codex,"pm validate --json showed missing_linked_paths: [dist, test/generator.test.mjs]. Fixed by editing toon files and re-registering with pm update --note --force."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:11:30.262Z",codex,Caused by TypeScript migration that renamed test/generator.test.mjs to test/generator.test.ts in earlier session.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:11:30.262Z",codex,"Always update pm item file references when renaming files. pm validate files check catches stale paths. Use pm update --file to add references (it appends, not replaces, so direct toon edits are sometimes needed)."
